    "description": "使用重力场 DLC 释放重力的力量！进入一个物理定律就是你的游乐场的世界，操纵自然力量来创造、控制和征服<br><br><strong>重力操纵</strong>：利用重力场的力量以前所未有的精度移动、举起和投掷物体。创造复杂的连锁反应，观察你的环境变得生动起来<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066050/extras/0b2cc3781e5f6374ed838defbe845b19.poster.avif?t=1722055636\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066050/extras/0b2cc3781e5f6374ed838defbe845b19.webm?t=1722055636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066050/extras/0b2cc3781e5f6374ed838defbe845b19.mp4?t=1722055636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>广阔的沙盒环境</strong>：探索充满互动物体的广阔景观。试验重力场并操纵周围环境<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066050/extras/58b47a643408212d033a8b0b3799ee5b.poster.avif?t=1722055636\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066050/extras/58b47a643408212d033a8b0b3799ee5b.webm?t=1722055636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066050/extras/58b47a643408212d033a8b0b3799ee5b.mp4?t=1722055636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>创新的游戏机制</strong>：利用重力来控制你周围的世界。当你的指尖掌握重力的力量时，可能性是无穷无尽的<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066050/extras/cc7d1fbceafe2c54ecbd0bb66139815b.poster.avif?t=1722055636\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066050/extras/cc7d1fbceafe2c54ecbd0bb66139815b.webm?t=1722055636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:/